## Findings
1. [P1] Fix 2a still keys pending orders off `'submitted'` - `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:467`, `:887`, and `:979` still compare `(status || '').toLowerCase() === 'submitted'`. Base44 uses `'new'` for fresh orders, so the `pending_unconfirmed` bucket stays empty and the pending badge never appears for new orders. FIX: change all three comparisons from `'submitted'` to `'new'`.
2. [P2] Fix 2b still renders the pending bucket first - `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:1094` keeps `const bucketOrder = ['pending_unconfirmed', 'served', 'in_progress']`, which renders `pending_unconfirmed` above `in_progress` instead of last. FIX: reorder the array so `pending_unconfirmed` renders after `in_progress`.
3. [P1] Fix 3 terminal screen state is not durable - the `isV8` "nothing waiting" branch is still rendered directly at `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:1014-1045`, but `terminalStateShownForVersion` has 0 hits and there is no `terminalVersion` or localStorage persistence for this screen. Reloading clears the terminal-state gate instead of preserving it for the current version. FIX: add the versioned localStorage-backed state, memo, and effect described in the task without changing the locked UI copy.
4. [P1] Fix 4 flat guest cards is still unimplemented - Section 5 at `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:917-1003` still renders one wrapper card with the `otherGuestsExpanded` toggle and `tr('cart.table_orders', ...)`, and `guestTotal` at `:949` still sums all guest orders without `isCancelledOrder`. The UI remains grouped instead of flat, and per-guest totals stay wrong when a guest has cancelled orders. FIX: remove the wrapper accordion, render `otherGuestIdsFromOrders.map((gid) => <Card key={gid}>...)` directly, and fold `isCancelledOrder(o)` into `guestTotal`.
5. [P2] Fix 5 footer is still the old filled CTA - the no-cart footer branch at `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:1303-1310` still renders a filled button with `className="w-full min-h-[44px] text-white"` and `style={{backgroundColor: primaryColor}}`; there is no `variant="outline"`, no `cart.cta.need_help_or_bill` helper copy, and no inline `Bell` helper row. FIX: replace this branch with the locked outline button wrapper and helper `<p>` using `tr('cart.cta.need_help_or_bill', ...)` plus `<Bell className="inline w-4 h-4 align-middle" />`.
6. [P1] Fix 6 table totals still include cancelled orders - `pages/PublicMenu/CartView.jsx:521-530` still sums every other-guest order into `tableOrdersTotal` and never calls `isCancelledOrder`, while `guestTotal` at `:949` also sums every order blindly. The table and guest totals remain inflated by cancelled orders. FIX: add the cancelled-order guard inside both reducers and include `isCancelledOrder` in the `tableOrdersTotal` memo dependency array.

